---
// Stack.astro
// Componente de Stack Tecnológico estilo Bento con Tailwind CSS
---

<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon@v2.15.1/devicon.min.css">

<section class="w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto p-4">
  
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
    
    <div class="md:col-span-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-50">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Frontend</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6">Creando interfaces de usuario interactivas, responsivas y optimizadas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-4xl text-gray-300">
        <i class="devicon-html5-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="HTML5"></i>
        <i class="devicon-css3-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="CSS3"></i>
        <i class="devicon-javascript-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="JavaScript"></i>
        <i class="devicon-typescript-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="TypeScript"></i>
        <i class="devicon-react-original colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="React"></i>
        <i class="devicon-astro-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Astro"></i>
        <i class="devicon-tailwindcss-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Tailwind CSS"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-3 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-50">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Backend</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-6">Desarrollo de lógica de servidor sólida, APIs REST y microservicios.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-4xl text-gray-300">
        <i class="devicon-nodejs-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Node.js"></i>
        <i class="devicon-express-original transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Express"></i>
        <i class="devicon-python-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Python"></i>
        <i class="devicon-java-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Java"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-45">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Base de Datos</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-4">Modelado de datos eficientes y persistencia segura.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-3xl text-gray-300">
        <i class="devicon-postgresql-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="PostgreSQL"></i>
        <i class="devicon-mongodb-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="MongoDB"></i>
        <i class="devicon-mysql-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="MySQL"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-45">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Herramientas</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-4">Control de versiones, despliegue y automatización.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-3xl text-gray-300">
        <i class="devicon-git-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Git"></i>
        <i class="devicon-github-original transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="GitHub"></i>
        <i class="devicon-docker-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Docker"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-2 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:border-white/20 hover:bg-white/10 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-45">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Diseño</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-4">Planificación visual, prototipado y experiencia de usuario.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 text-3xl text-gray-300">
        <i class="devicon-figma-plain colored transition-transform hover:scale-110" title="Figma"></i>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>